Set Height 750
Source "recordings/tapes/shared-config.tape"
Output "recordings/svgs/toolkits/search-google-limit-1.svg"
Output "recordings/ascii/toolkits/search-google-limit-1.ascii"

Hide
Type "# Search with --limit flag"
Enter
Show
Type "composio toolkits search google --limit 1"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 6s
